CHECK_ATOMIC

dnl Unless the user specified OBJCXX, force it to be the same as CXX. This ensures
dnl that we get the same -std flags for both.
m4_ifdef([AC_PROG_OBJCXX],[
if test "x${OBJCXX+set}" = "x"; then
  OBJCXX="${CXX}"
fi
AC_PROG_OBJCXX
])

dnl Libtool init checks.
